						<summary>

						<p>Pillar of a <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> at the foot of the Rāmalingēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1530, Rākshasa, Kārttika śu. 11</hi> corresponding <hi rend="bold">1608 A.D., November 8 Tuesday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records the consecration of the images of the deities Lakshmī and others and the setting up of the pillars for the swing <hi rend="italic">(uyyāla)</hi> by Kannelūri Pāpaya Aṅkamaṁgāru at Brahmaguṇḍam in Yeṟṟabālem.</p>						

						</summary>
